10$^{9}$Msolar and the case with M$_{BH}$ = 10$^{11}$
Msolar. (iii) The resultant LFs at NIR are dominated by black holes at
L$_{I,J}$ {\lt}\~{} 10$^{44}$ erg s$^{-1}$, and by
